                        <interp inst="t18470816-name-290" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470816-name-290" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD SMITH.</persName>
                  </hi> I live at Dock-head, Bermondsey. On the 2nd of Aug., about six o'clock, I was on London-bridge, looking at a rowing-match—I missed my pocket-handkerchief, turned, and saw Palmer with it in his possession—this produced is it—it is mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
