                  <hi rend="italic">Palmer. Q.</hi> Did you see me try to pick pockets? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No, not you—the other one <hi rend="italic">works.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Palmer's Defence.</hi> There was a rowing-match; I was standing, with my hands together; I had something put into my hand; the gentleman turned, and said, "You have got my handkerchief;" I took it out of my trowsers pocket, and gave it him.</p>
